Event.Message: The print router failed to initialize. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.

The system failed to initialize the local print provider: Error %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.

The system failed to impersonate the client: Error %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.
The system failed to initialize the name cache: Error %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.
Failed to initialize the router cache: Error %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.
The print spooler cannot start because the PrinterBusEnumerator could not start. Error code %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.

The print spooler failed to load print provider %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.
InitializePrintProvider failed for provider %1. This can occur because of system instability or a lack of system resources.

Event.Message: Group Policy was unable to delete per computer printer connection %1. Error %2. The printer connection is still available to users on this computer. Group Policy will periodically retry deleting the printer connection.
